item.title: 【BLU-RAY】BD REMUX - Slipknot {Sic}nesses Live at Download 2010 1080i BluRay AVC REMUX DTS-HD MA 5.1-SiGLA
item.description:
​

Description: {sic}nesses was filmed in high definition when Slipknot headlined the Download Festival in front of 80,000 fans in June 2009. Among the band's many legendary live shows, this performance remains a career highlight and a fitting tribute to bassist and founding member Paul Gray (#2) who died the following year. Originally released by Roadrunner as a 2DVD set in September 2010, this concert is now released on Blu-ray, with newly remixed DTS 5.1 surround sound, so that Slipknot can be seen and heard like never before. The concert was filmed with 30 cameras and premiered in selected theaters for free across the US, on it's release in 2010.
